<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l8">Nu als <expan>derſ<ex>elb</ex></expan> Sebolt <expan>pfıncʒ<ex>ing</ex></expan> . von <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>gnedıgıſt<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> ~ dem künıg deſmals </ab>
