<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l15"><expan>gecʒog<ex>en</ex></expan> vnd nu heim ſein . Daʒ vılleıht nıht notdurft <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan> . daʒ wır vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l16">ʒu dem dıenſt <expan>ſchık<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>ſolt<ex>en</ex></expan> . <expan>Bıtt<ex>en</ex></expan> wır eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> <expan>fleıſſıkl<ex>ich</ex></expan> / vns </ab>
