<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l19">daʒ wır niht <expan>v<ex>er</ex>vnglimpft</expan> <expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan> . Vnd was eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ın den <expan>ſache<ex>n</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l20">geraten <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>notdürft<ex>en</ex></expan> deẅcht <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> Jr erfürt daʒ Jr vns das bey <expan>dıſ<ex>em</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l21"><expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>verſchr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet ſo ſchıerıſt ır mugt . daʒ wır vns darnach <expan>wıſſ<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
