<ab facs="#facs_171_r1l23">vmb eẅr <expan>erſamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> allcʒeıt <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dıenen</expan> <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> . <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> vrbanj </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_171" id="85v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Pfarr<ex>er</ex></expan> zu sand Sebolt </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersamer und lieber <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan>, uns hat
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> lieber <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
                        und <expan>ratg<ex>esell</ex></expan> Sebolt
                            <expan>Pfincz<ex>ing</ex></expan> wol gesagt, wie ir im, als er nehst zu
                        Costencz <expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, von des diensts
                                <expan>weg<ex>en,</ex></expan> den wir
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, dem <expan>römisch<ex>en</ex></expan> künig,
                        auf <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>czog</expan>
<expan>Fridr<ex>ich</ex></expan> von <expan>Österr<ex>eich</ex></expan>, tun
                                <expan>sölt<ex>en</ex></expan>, gar hilfflich und
                                <expan>fürderl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<expan>gewes<ex>en</ex></expan> seyt, des und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan> und trewen, die ir uns beweiset,
                                <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan> wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit <expan>sund<ex>er</ex>m</expan> fleiss
                        und <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, das umb ewch zu
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schulde<ex>n</ex></expan>. Nu als
                                <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Sebolt
                            <expan>Pfincz<ex>ing</ex></expan> von <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>gnedigist<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> dem künig, desmals
                            <expan>geschid<ex>en</ex></expan> ist, daz wir im l mit gleven zu dienst
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>, die auf den <app>
<note><q type="date">mentag vor sand <expan>Johan<ex>n</ex>s</expan> tag
                                    schierist</q>17.06.1415</note>
</app> bey uns von hawse <expan>ausreit<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>solt<ex>en,</ex></expan> und <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> wir an
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren,</expan> burggraf <expan>Fridr<ex>ich,</ex></expan>
                        brief uns geschikt und auch an zweyn <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>geschrift<ex>en</ex></expan> wol <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan>
<expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> der künig, mit dem
                                <expan>vorg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> von <expan>Österr<ex>eich</ex></expan>
                        berichtet sey, so <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan> wir sust in der gemein,
                        daz <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> reichs stett volk vom velt
                                <expan>geczog<ex>en</ex></expan> und nu heim sein, daz villeiht niht
                        notdurft <expan>w<ex>er</ex>e</expan>, daz wir uns zu dem dienst
                                <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>solt<ex>en</ex></expan>, <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr
                                <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>fleissikl<ex>ich,</ex></expan> uns <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> rat
                                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> zu lassen
                            <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ein <expan>erfaru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> zu
                        tun, wie uns, wa ewch das <expan>all<ex>er</ex></expan> füklichst und
                        bekemlichst dunket, wie wir uns in den <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>hielte<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz wir niht
                            <expan>v<ex>er</ex>unglimpft</expan>
<expan>wurde<ex>n</ex></expan>. Und was ewr
                            <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> in den <expan>sache<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        geraten <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>notdürft<ex>en</ex></expan> dewcht <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> ir
                        erfürt, daz ir uns das bey <expan>dis<ex>em</ex></expan>
<expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>eiben</ex></expan> wellet, so schierist ir mugt, daz wir
                        uns darnach <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> zu
                            <expan>richte<ex>n</ex></expan>. Daran beweiset ir uns sölich lieb und
                                <expan>frewnts<ex>chaft</ex></expan>, die wir umb ewr
                                <expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> allczeit
                            <expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>v<ex>er</ex>dienen</expan>
<expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>sab<ex>at</ex>o</expan> Urbani. </ab>
</div>
</div></body>
